data.title: Ahmet Zeki Soydemir
data.meta_description: Ahmet Zeki Soydemir was an officer of the Ottoman Army and a general of the Turkish Army. The division under the command of Soydemir was one of the first to capture Smyrna from the Greek Army during the Turkish War of Independence.
